What we need to first: 
-  Create the DB table..-- on top of this i want to create the RAP application..



Short cut -->
Navigate one object to another-- select the object -->press f3 -- it will navigate to specific selected structure.

right click on dictionary --> click on Database table - create table..
  table-zdbt_trav.
@AbapCatalog.label: 'Travel db table'
@AbapCatalog.enhancementCategory : #NOT_EXTENSIBLE
@AbapCatalog.tableCategory : #TRANSPARENT
@AbapCatalog.deliveryClass : #A
@AbapCatalog.dataMaintenance : #RESTRICTED
define table zdbt_Trav{
  kay client : abap.clnt not null;
  key travel_id : /dmo/travel_id not null;
  description : /dmo/description;
  status : /dmo/travel_status

// timestampe fields
   lastchangedat : timestampl;
}

Now create the rap applicaation -- right click on table -- click on generate abap repository objects. 
